{"author":"Iso Tester","data":{"body":"Persistence AC hardened: stateful Gerrit site subdirs are now EXTERNAL named volumes (gerrit_git/index/cache/db/etc/logs/plugins, all external: true) created by compose-up.sh via 'docker volume create' (local bind onto /var/gerrit/site/* on the EBS volume) BEFORE 'docker compose up'. 'docker compose down -v' cannot destroy them; baked binaries not shadowed (per-subdir, not whole /var/gerrit). Verified: after down/up the admin SSH clone still succeeds (data persisted)."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1782786982458294001,"uuid":"7c52336e-d167-46ff-adba-59b91b35646c"}